WEBVTT

00:07.520 --> 00:08.920
‎SAY NO TO PIRACY, SUPPORT ORIGINALS

01:36.800 --> 01:42.920
‎ADAPTED FROM XI XING’S NOVEL
<i>‎QUEEN CHU</i>‎ ON QIDIAN.COM

02:00.560 --> 02:02.040
<i>Dispatch Rider's Tally.</i>

02:20.000 --> 02:22.520
This is how the frontier troops
tie their prisoners.

02:23.680 --> 02:26.520
Could it be betrayal from within?

02:30.520 --> 02:31.800
We're dispatch riders from Wangcheng.

02:31.880 --> 02:34.960
The bandits changed into our uniforms
and went to Beicao Post House.

02:37.000 --> 02:39.800
<i>That post house leads directly</i>
<i>to Yunzhong Prefecture.</i>

02:45.000 --> 02:48.360
Judging by your grace and bearing,
you are no ordinary commoner.

02:48.440 --> 02:50.120
How did you end up in this plight?

02:51.400 --> 02:55.320
My mother dotes on me
and wants me to look refined

02:55.920 --> 02:57.280
so that I might be treated
with more respect

02:58.120 --> 02:59.640
once I marry into another family.

03:01.720 --> 03:03.160
The wilderness is no place

03:04.000 --> 03:05.600
for a lady to wander.

03:09.480 --> 03:10.640
If we were to encounter bandits,

03:11.240 --> 03:13.320
the dispatches you carry
are worth far more than I am.

03:13.840 --> 03:16.280
The roads are rough at night,
and you're out here alone.

03:16.960 --> 03:18.320
If you cross paths with the outlaws,

03:18.840 --> 03:21.800
you will find yourself
completely left to your fate.

03:22.920 --> 03:24.880
If something actually happens to you,

03:25.720 --> 03:27.160
it'll be too late to wish you hadn't.

03:28.520 --> 03:32.800
You are a woman as well,
so if you are not afraid, why should I be?

03:39.040 --> 03:41.360
<i>When you speak,</i>
<i>there is no prominence in your throat,</i>

03:42.280 --> 03:43.880
<i>and the angle of your radius is smooth.</i>

03:44.720 --> 03:47.000
<i>The pauldrons of your chainmail</i>
<i>hang three cun lower than they should,</i>

03:47.080 --> 03:49.320
<i>which means your shoulders are narrower</i>
<i>than those of a typical male soldier.</i>

03:50.360 --> 03:52.080
<i>Your knees tuck inward,</i>

03:52.160 --> 03:53.600
<i>and when you get off a horse,</i>
<i>your toes touch the ground first,</i>

03:53.680 --> 03:54.800
<i>rather than the soles of your feet.</i>

03:55.320 --> 03:58.120
<i>It's an ingrained instinct or a woman</i>
<i>to lift her hem to shun the dirt.</i>

03:59.680 --> 04:02.800
Your flaw lies not in your disguise
but in your habits.

04:03.440 --> 04:05.800
Ma'am, your disguise is flawless,

04:05.880 --> 04:09.000
but your old habits can't be faked.

04:10.200 --> 04:12.280
You knew all along
we weren't dispatch riders?

04:13.200 --> 04:14.880
I grew up in the army.

04:15.400 --> 04:16.880
No one knows soldiers better than I do.

04:18.079 --> 04:19.040
Moreover,

04:19.760 --> 04:22.640
you don't act like dispatch riders,

04:23.400 --> 04:24.440
but more like bandits.

04:26.280 --> 04:30.360
Since you have already seen through us,
why did you still choose to come along?

04:31.240 --> 04:33.200
Aren't you doing the same thing?

04:34.520 --> 04:37.520
Her vow of "My life is worth it"
still exposed us.

04:37.600 --> 04:41.000
You saw through me long ago,
yet you still let me follow you…

04:42.640 --> 04:44.120
because you wanted something from me.

04:54.560 --> 04:56.320
You're sharp.

04:56.400 --> 04:57.720
But it's a pity.

04:58.440 --> 05:01.360
The sharp ones never live long.

05:06.280 --> 05:07.160
What?

05:08.040 --> 05:09.200
Are you trying to take my life?

05:10.080 --> 05:11.160
At the post house,

05:12.240 --> 05:14.480
I saw right through the charade
you and that woman staged.

05:14.560 --> 05:15.920
Yet I brought you along anyway

05:16.520 --> 05:22.400
to see exactly what you hoped to gain
from such an elaborate ruse.

05:35.600 --> 05:36.440
Put down your blade.

05:39.920 --> 05:42.720
I said, put it down.

05:45.560 --> 05:46.760
Jiu.

05:48.080 --> 05:49.200
Who exactly are you?

05:52.400 --> 05:55.560
You posed as dispatch riders
to intercept intelligence

05:56.080 --> 05:57.040
concerning the Northern Desert.

05:58.440 --> 06:00.440
Chu Ling, the Guard General,
has always been invincible.

06:00.520 --> 06:02.920
It's impossible for a Northern Desert
squad to have exploited such a gap

06:03.000 --> 06:05.440
unless someone leaked the dispatch.

06:06.680 --> 06:07.720
How do you know that?

06:08.600 --> 06:10.160
But if you are not closely related,

06:10.880 --> 06:12.200
why go to such lengths?

06:15.160 --> 06:16.440
Unless…

06:18.200 --> 06:19.200
you are from the Northern Desert.

06:19.920 --> 06:23.560
They could never have crossed
Yunzhong Prefecture.

06:27.720 --> 06:29.080
We are from Cangmu Stronghold.

06:36.800 --> 06:40.080
We also suspected
that someone leaked the dispatch.

06:40.600 --> 06:42.000
That is why we targeted
the dispatch riders.

06:42.600 --> 06:45.560
We wanted to find out who at court

06:45.640 --> 06:48.600
is colluding with the Northern Desert
to threaten Yunzhong Prefecture.

06:48.680 --> 06:50.040
Cangmu Stronghold
has always been a mystery,

06:50.120 --> 06:51.240
known to but a few.

06:52.040 --> 06:54.480
Moreover, you never meddle
in the affairs of the court.

06:55.600 --> 06:57.000
Why start interfering now?

06:57.800 --> 06:59.800
I heard during General Chu's campaign
against bandits,

06:59.880 --> 07:02.920
he killed your former leader, Mu Mianhong.

07:03.000 --> 07:03.840
Shouldn't you resent him?

07:04.440 --> 07:05.440
Why help him now?

07:06.360 --> 07:08.080
We may be nothing more than bandits,

07:09.120 --> 07:12.960
but we do know the nation comes
before personal grudges.

07:13.880 --> 07:16.240
General Chu has guarded
Yunzhong for 20 years,

07:16.840 --> 07:18.160
keeping the State of Chu in peace.

07:19.200 --> 07:21.200
If someone in the court

07:21.280 --> 07:24.120
colludes with the Northern Desert
to frame him,

07:24.200 --> 07:25.040
the country will be in peril.

07:26.360 --> 07:28.280
As will Cangmu Stronghold.

07:34.600 --> 07:37.240
To be honest, I am Chu Ling's daughter.

07:39.280 --> 07:42.080
I heard my father was gravely ill
and was rushing to Yunzhong Prefecture.

07:42.920 --> 07:44.760
I encountered some trouble on the road.

07:45.280 --> 07:48.040
I had no choice but to disguise myself
and join the dispatch riders.

07:54.360 --> 07:56.720
If you two are in trouble
and need a place to hide,

07:58.680 --> 08:00.200
would you like to follow me back
to the Stronghold?

08:10.800 --> 08:14.000
Sir, just stopping for a quick bite
or a night's stay?

08:14.600 --> 08:16.360
Have you seen any women
bound for Yunzhong Prefecture today?

08:16.440 --> 08:19.080
There have been plenty of caravans
and women as well.

08:19.600 --> 08:21.120
Which one are you referring to, exactly?

08:27.440 --> 08:30.040
A runaway maid who stole from her master.

08:30.840 --> 08:32.919
She is fair and tender,
bearing no mark of toil.

08:33.000 --> 08:35.720
Few maids dare travel this desolate trail.

08:35.799 --> 08:38.039
Let alone a soft-skinned lady like that.

08:41.679 --> 08:43.679
-Never seen one.
-Liar.

08:44.240 --> 08:45.080
-You've seen her.
-Officer, please calm down!

08:45.160 --> 08:46.640
Where is she?

08:47.160 --> 08:48.320
Let me think.

08:50.040 --> 08:51.600
I remember now. There was such a girl.

08:51.680 --> 08:53.160
She stayed here a couple of days ago,

08:53.240 --> 08:55.360
claiming she was visiting kin
in Yunzhong Prefecture.

08:55.440 --> 08:57.320
Later, she left with the dispatch riders.

08:57.400 --> 08:58.840
I don't know where she went after that.

09:00.320 --> 09:02.000
But I do know where her mother is.

09:02.760 --> 09:04.080
-Her mother?
-Yes.

09:04.160 --> 09:06.800
Her mother hired a carriage
and went back to the village herself.

09:07.520 --> 09:09.240
From that livery stable
three li north of here.

09:22.080 --> 09:23.840
-Come back!
-No, I won't…

09:23.920 --> 09:25.040
-Officer.
-Despicable wretch!

09:25.120 --> 09:26.320
You owe me a fortune!

09:26.400 --> 09:27.440
You…!

09:31.760 --> 09:34.560
A few days ago,
did a girl named Fu come through here?

09:35.240 --> 09:37.120
Officer, what do you mean?

09:37.200 --> 09:40.680
We get so many girls passing through,
how could I remember every name?

09:40.760 --> 09:41.800
Don't play dumb.

09:42.880 --> 09:46.240
She paid you to put on an act
and then left with the dispatch riders,

09:46.760 --> 09:48.240
-didn't she?
-Yes.

09:48.320 --> 09:50.800
She tricked those dispatch riders,
and they headed for Yunzhong.

09:58.160 --> 09:59.400
Good.

10:00.360 --> 10:02.400
Seems you are destined to die.

10:18.760 --> 10:20.440
This forest reeks of something foul.

10:21.200 --> 10:23.480
The traps and mechanisms
must be over a hundred.

10:24.960 --> 10:28.480
This is far too elaborate
for a mere stronghold of bandits.

10:30.560 --> 10:31.720
Are they truly trustworthy?

10:33.160 --> 10:34.400
I'm not sure.

10:34.480 --> 10:35.840
Then why did you insist on coming?

10:41.480 --> 10:42.720
Madam Ge wasn't lying.

10:43.400 --> 10:45.960
Her story matches perfectly
with what I knew of the past.

10:46.880 --> 10:51.160
It seems Cangmu Stronghold wasn't always
at odds with my father,

10:51.240 --> 10:52.600
despite what rumors say.

10:53.280 --> 10:54.960
Tie Ying is no fool.

10:55.040 --> 10:57.440
My tricks will only last
half a day at most.

10:58.080 --> 10:59.480
We are outnumbered.

10:59.560 --> 11:00.600
A head-on fight is not the best course.

11:01.200 --> 11:03.080
We'd better seek refuge
in Cangmu Stronghold

11:03.160 --> 11:05.360
and plan our next move
after scouting the truth.

11:07.600 --> 11:10.560
So, you're still gambling.

11:11.320 --> 11:13.760
I dared to risk
only because you stood by me.

11:29.840 --> 11:30.960
Don't get cocky.

11:31.680 --> 11:33.320
Last night, you were clearly defenseless,

11:34.040 --> 11:35.720
yet you still chose
to provoke the bandits.

11:36.840 --> 11:39.280
Do you realize,
if I'd been a moment later,

11:39.360 --> 11:40.800
you'd be a corpse by now?

11:41.320 --> 11:42.800
If they wanted me dead,

11:42.880 --> 11:46.000
they would have struck
when I exposed Madam Ge's disguise.

11:47.680 --> 11:48.880
Is that why you risked your life?

11:50.280 --> 11:54.520
Her taking men disguised
as dispatch riders to steal the dispatch

11:54.600 --> 11:58.320
isn't to hurt my father
but to uncover the truth.

11:58.840 --> 12:01.680
In other words, she truly is helping him.

12:02.800 --> 12:03.840
Aren't you afraid

12:04.360 --> 12:06.160
you've jumped out of the frying pan
and straight into the fire?

12:06.920 --> 12:11.320
Isn't that just what we do every day?

12:24.560 --> 12:26.080
CANGMU STRONGHOLD

12:26.160 --> 12:27.720
-Ge is back.
-Ge's returned.

12:27.800 --> 12:28.840
-Ge.
-Madam.

12:28.920 --> 12:29.960
-Madam is back.
-Ge.

12:31.000 --> 12:32.240
-Ge.
-Welcome back.

12:32.320 --> 12:33.240
Ge.

12:33.320 --> 12:34.280
Let me take that.

12:34.360 --> 12:35.520
Ge.

12:37.360 --> 12:38.280
Aunt.

12:39.640 --> 12:42.360
-Laosan, we have guests.
-Coming.

12:44.600 --> 12:47.280
This is my younger brother, Ge Laosan,
leader of Cangmu Stronghold.

12:48.040 --> 12:49.240
Greetings, Mr. Ge.

12:49.320 --> 12:50.800
‎GE LAOSAN, CANGMU STRONGHOLD

12:51.520 --> 12:52.480
Xiaoman.

12:52.560 --> 12:53.480
‎XIAOMAN, CANGMU STRONGHOLD

12:54.320 --> 12:55.240
Take a seat.

12:56.320 --> 12:57.920
Why'd you bring two strangers back?

13:00.000 --> 13:01.000
We need a place to lie low for a while.

13:01.080 --> 13:02.080
Lie low?

13:02.600 --> 13:05.200
How should I address you two?

13:05.800 --> 13:07.760
He's Jiu. I'm Fu.

13:08.360 --> 13:09.680
Fu.

13:10.200 --> 13:11.720
Good name.

13:12.360 --> 13:14.040
Sounds like good fortune.

13:17.000 --> 13:19.800
Madam Ge, there's something I need to ask.

13:19.880 --> 13:21.560
I know what it is.

13:22.160 --> 13:23.200
Don't worry.

13:23.720 --> 13:25.640
You saw it for yourselves on the way in.

13:26.280 --> 13:29.520
We are known as Cangmu Stronghold,
hidden deep within these woods.

13:30.160 --> 13:31.520
There's a saying down the mountain,

13:31.600 --> 13:34.200
"Once you go deep into Cangmu Forest,
there's no way out."

13:34.800 --> 13:37.920
This forest is vast and deep,
a fortress built by nature itself.

13:38.000 --> 13:40.160
And we have all those hidden mechanisms
and traps.

13:40.240 --> 13:43.760
With bamboo nets overhead
and vine-traps underfoot,

13:43.840 --> 13:45.360
all life is barred from entry,

13:45.440 --> 13:46.800
be it human or beast.

13:46.880 --> 13:49.720
Here, you're safer than anywhere outside.

13:50.440 --> 13:52.480
If this place is so secret,

13:53.240 --> 13:55.520
how could you trust us enough
to let us in?

13:56.520 --> 13:57.480
Aren't you afraid?

13:57.560 --> 13:59.840
We value fate above all.

13:59.920 --> 14:02.160
I've trusted you, so I won't question it.

14:06.160 --> 14:08.640
Xiaoman, see to our guests.

14:08.720 --> 14:11.680
Once things calm down out there,
you can resume your journey.

14:13.640 --> 14:14.480
My gratitude, ma'am.

14:16.360 --> 14:17.440
Apologies for the intrusion.

14:17.520 --> 14:19.680
No trouble at all.

14:20.400 --> 14:21.320
This way, please.

14:24.080 --> 14:26.480
Have a good rest.

14:31.440 --> 14:32.360
She…?

14:48.800 --> 14:50.080
Mr. Tie!

14:50.600 --> 14:51.680
Mr. Tie.

14:54.520 --> 14:55.960
Mr. Tie. Something's wrong.

14:56.040 --> 14:57.600
The dispatch riders we were pursuing,
along with the Grand Princess,

14:57.680 --> 15:00.280
have vanished without a trace
near Cangmu Stronghold.

15:01.160 --> 15:02.280
The men we dispatched in pursuit

15:02.360 --> 15:04.680
were all slain
by the bandits of the stronghold.

15:05.720 --> 15:06.960
Cangmu Stronghold?

15:08.040 --> 15:11.880
I promised His Highness
to bring back Chu Zhao's head.

15:13.640 --> 15:15.400
Hear my command.

15:15.480 --> 15:17.720
Pick up the pace
and march into Cangmu Forest.

15:17.800 --> 15:19.680
Leave no one alive.

15:19.760 --> 15:24.360
I'd like to see what these remnants think
they can do to shield her.

15:35.080 --> 15:39.000
They offered you shelter,
and now you're raiding their armory?

15:39.080 --> 15:40.280
Cangmu Forest is vast and deep.

15:40.360 --> 15:42.640
They seem hospitable enough,

15:42.720 --> 15:45.760
but how could we truly rest easy
without investigating first?

15:47.000 --> 15:47.840
I didn't realize,

15:47.920 --> 15:50.200
though new to the jianghu,
you would think further ahead than I.

15:52.000 --> 15:52.960
Look at this.

15:55.000 --> 15:56.320
Careful.

16:02.400 --> 16:03.520
Seven modifications to the mechanism.

16:03.600 --> 16:07.280
Range increased by two zhang,
with less recoil.

16:08.600 --> 16:11.200
These are modified crossbows
the frontier troops used

16:11.280 --> 16:12.400
against the Northern Desert.

16:13.600 --> 16:14.640
How do you know?

16:14.720 --> 16:16.120
Back when I was in the army,

16:16.200 --> 16:18.320
I modified over 200
of these crossbows for the General.

16:19.840 --> 16:22.320
Mu Mianhong was killed
by my father, after all.

16:23.080 --> 16:26.200
So why would her stronghold
have weapons from the frontier troops?

16:26.800 --> 16:27.760
It's not just that.

16:28.800 --> 16:30.360
While searching for you,

16:30.440 --> 16:32.120
I saved a dispatch rider
who had been kidnapped by Madam Ge.

16:33.200 --> 16:34.640
<i>The knots used to tie him up</i>

16:35.680 --> 16:37.600
<i>were standard frontier troop rigging.</i>

16:38.200 --> 16:39.880
You mean…?

16:39.960 --> 16:41.080
Perhaps

16:41.840 --> 16:44.280
your father wasn't here
to suppress bandits.

16:44.360 --> 16:45.880
What are you implying?

16:45.960 --> 16:48.680
-Are you suggesting my father…?
-Wait for me.

16:57.760 --> 16:58.760
I won't be long.

17:55.600 --> 17:56.720
Your Highness,

17:57.720 --> 17:59.160
this feels a little too personal.

18:01.320 --> 18:02.920
Back when I left the Capital,

18:03.000 --> 18:05.400
who was it that swore
to guard the imperial city for me?

18:12.280 --> 18:15.200
I know it's because you care about me.

18:18.280 --> 18:21.920
But Xie Yanfang wouldn't release you
without expecting something in return.

18:23.440 --> 18:24.680
What's the situation at court?

18:25.200 --> 18:27.920
He'll look after Yu.

18:28.880 --> 18:32.120
But he needs the Grand Princess Token
to keep Deng Yi on a leash.

18:34.560 --> 18:35.960
So I handed it over.

18:43.520 --> 18:44.600
Indeed.

18:45.640 --> 18:47.160
Your brother

18:47.680 --> 18:49.760
has never been one to show his hand
without a guaranteed win.

18:51.240 --> 18:52.520
If you're not in the Capital,

18:53.280 --> 18:56.120
he's the only one who can keep Yu safe.

19:01.640 --> 19:02.880
Your wounds have yet to heal.

19:02.960 --> 19:04.000
You need proper rest.

19:07.800 --> 19:08.920
Just get some sleep.

19:24.880 --> 19:28.840
They… only gave us one room?

19:33.960 --> 19:34.920
I insisted on this.

19:37.440 --> 19:39.000
With such grave injuries,

19:40.440 --> 19:42.000
you need to stay close to me.

19:42.920 --> 19:44.440
Or how am I supposed to protect you?

20:00.400 --> 20:01.800
And how will you protect me exactly?

20:22.920 --> 20:24.040
It's a cold night.

20:25.960 --> 20:27.320
Your wounds won't heal if you freeze.

20:32.560 --> 20:33.640
Keep warm.

20:48.640 --> 20:50.680
Are you out of your mind?

20:51.640 --> 20:54.920
You knew who she was
and you still brought her here?

21:08.080 --> 21:09.800
They're not to be trifled with.

21:10.960 --> 21:14.640
Xiao Xun's ambushes
always have a deeper kill.

21:15.560 --> 21:17.960
That guard at the gate
sent word in the White Wolf tongue,

21:19.080 --> 21:20.640
saying the pursuers
have all been eliminated.

21:21.560 --> 21:25.280
If they were with Xiao Xun,
why would they kill their own?

21:26.120 --> 21:27.600
I didn't know you could speak that tongue.

21:28.600 --> 21:31.240
My father taught me
when we were in the desert.

21:33.400 --> 21:39.280
No one knows that except him.

21:40.160 --> 21:41.800
But what if it's all just an act?

21:42.480 --> 21:44.680
Xiao Xun's men have no reason
to slaughter their own.

21:45.280 --> 21:48.560
Given how cautious Deng Yi is,

21:49.160 --> 21:51.960
he'd never trust a band of bandits
who still answer to their old master.

21:52.040 --> 21:53.120
He wouldn't trust them.

21:54.080 --> 21:56.520
And Xie Yanfang? Even less likely.

21:58.440 --> 22:01.360
Whether Madam Ge and the others respect
my father or fear him,

22:02.920 --> 22:04.080
at the very least,

22:05.680 --> 22:09.200
my father never bore them any ill will.

22:10.280 --> 22:14.480
I still find it hard to believe
they've suddenly turned into saints.

22:15.240 --> 22:19.240
Are you willing to take a gamble with me?

22:20.200 --> 22:21.680
What if we lose?

22:31.040 --> 22:33.040
At least on the road to the afterlife,

22:34.400 --> 22:35.560
you'll keep me company.

22:41.880 --> 22:42.800
TAIJI HALL

22:42.880 --> 22:46.120
Recently, our dispatch riders
were ambushed near the Beicao Post House.

22:46.200 --> 22:48.800
Investigations confirm that this was
the work of the Cangmu Stronghold.

22:48.880 --> 22:51.800
This is an absolute outrage.

22:51.880 --> 22:53.200
-Utterly preposterous.
-Indeed.

22:53.280 --> 22:55.880
Chu Ling's leniency
allowed these bandits to flourish.

22:55.960 --> 22:58.720
Now, the remnants of that stronghold
have the audacity

22:58.800 --> 23:01.720
to pose as our dispatch riders
to steal vital military intelligence.

23:02.320 --> 23:03.760
Your Majesty, I implore you

23:03.840 --> 23:05.480
to issue a decree for a full investigation

23:05.560 --> 23:07.080
and ensure that justice is served.

23:07.920 --> 23:10.520
General Chu marched against the bandits
on imperial command.

23:10.600 --> 23:13.560
When the bandit leader, Mu Mianhong,
took her life by leaping from the cliff,

23:13.640 --> 23:14.840
he refused to harm
even the women and children

23:14.920 --> 23:16.240
remaining in the stronghold.

23:16.760 --> 23:20.680
To think that such benevolence
is being wielded against him?

23:20.760 --> 23:21.920
Well…

23:22.560 --> 23:24.960
Your Majesty, an urgent report
has just arrived.

23:25.040 --> 23:26.760
The Northern Desert
dispatched an envoy to Yunzhong,

23:26.840 --> 23:28.720
only for General Chu
to execute him on the spot.

23:29.320 --> 23:31.920
Tensions between the two states
are already high.

23:32.000 --> 23:33.560
What are we to do now?

23:33.640 --> 23:36.720
Even in war,
one does not kill a messenger.

23:36.800 --> 23:40.040
This act will surely incite them
to take up arms.

23:40.120 --> 23:42.280
The charge of leniency toward bandits
might be overlooked,

23:42.360 --> 23:45.520
but inciting a war is unpardonable.

23:46.440 --> 23:48.960
First, they breached our frontier.

23:49.040 --> 23:51.600
Then, their envoy infiltrated
the General's tent

23:51.680 --> 23:53.680
with a secret letter at night.

23:54.320 --> 23:56.080
If that isn't espionage, then what is?

23:56.160 --> 23:57.880
Mr. Deng is correct.

23:58.640 --> 24:00.600
The General has commanded
the frontier troops for decades,

24:00.680 --> 24:01.720
with his defenses impregnable.

24:01.800 --> 24:03.640
If they nearly faltered last time,

24:03.720 --> 24:05.480
it must be because a spy
leaked our positions.

24:06.520 --> 24:09.680
Desperate times demand desperate measures.

24:10.280 --> 24:11.280
According to our laws,

24:11.360 --> 24:14.520
when a threat is imminent and unclear,
one may act first and report thereafter.

24:15.360 --> 24:17.080
So how can General Chu be blamed?

24:20.000 --> 24:22.880
Your Majesty, General Chu
is advanced in years.

24:23.480 --> 24:25.520
As the frontier defenses
have seen repeated breaches,

24:25.600 --> 24:27.760
I beg Your Majesty
to appoint another worthy general.

24:29.680 --> 24:31.840
These concerns are not without merit.

24:31.920 --> 24:35.120
As the Northern Desert stirs
with ambition, we must fortify

24:35.840 --> 24:39.000
the frontier in anticipation of conflict.

24:40.480 --> 24:42.360
As for the selection of a successor,

24:44.760 --> 24:46.680
it remains a matter
for His Majesty's judgment.

24:47.280 --> 24:49.640
The General has held Yunzhong
for 20 years.

24:49.720 --> 24:52.520
Each time the enemy dared to invade,
they were repelled in ignominious defeat.

24:53.640 --> 24:55.800
In your candidate list,

24:55.880 --> 24:59.440
how many can truly rival
his illustrious record?

25:00.040 --> 25:01.800
A commander of such stature
is not cultivated overnight.

25:01.880 --> 25:06.320
Yet, the security of the frontier
cannot be staked upon a single individual.

25:07.880 --> 25:09.280
Mr. Xie, please set your mind at rest.

25:09.360 --> 25:12.440
I shall confer with the ministers

25:12.520 --> 25:16.680
to select the most fitting candidate
for Yunzhong Prefecture

25:17.560 --> 25:19.520
to alleviate the General's burdens.

25:25.760 --> 25:29.000
<i>What a masterful move he's played.</i>

25:47.080 --> 25:48.000
This is…

25:49.200 --> 25:50.040
Sand Fox Whistle.

25:50.120 --> 25:51.400
That's right.

25:52.160 --> 25:54.080
This is a frontier troop alert
for cavalry raids.

25:56.320 --> 25:57.840
Stubborn, aren't you?

25:57.920 --> 25:58.920
BROTHERS IN ARMS, WISE IN DEED

25:59.000 --> 26:00.120
Talk.

26:00.680 --> 26:01.760
If you won't,

26:02.440 --> 26:05.600
I'll chop you to pieces
and feed you to the wolves in the hills.

26:05.680 --> 26:08.200
-Throw him to the wolves!
-Throw him to the wolves!

26:08.280 --> 26:09.320
Talk or not?

26:12.120 --> 26:13.240
What are you doing here?

26:14.160 --> 26:15.560
I'm in the middle of something.

26:15.640 --> 26:16.480
Don't mind me.

26:17.160 --> 26:18.400
Leave him to me.

26:27.600 --> 26:29.520
-That's pretty brutal.
-Indeed.

26:29.600 --> 26:31.280
-Listen to the scream.
-Right.

26:32.160 --> 26:33.360
What is he doing?

26:33.440 --> 26:36.280
That's brutal.

26:36.800 --> 26:38.760
Tell me about it!

26:38.840 --> 26:40.640
Brutal…

26:45.200 --> 26:47.160
Didn't see that coming. He's good.

26:49.720 --> 26:51.880
-Well?
-He talked.

26:52.480 --> 26:55.960
They entered Cangmu Forest yesterday
and located Cangmu Stronghold.

26:56.040 --> 26:58.040
Their men will arrive tonight.

26:58.120 --> 26:59.120
We should prepare in advance.

26:59.880 --> 27:01.360
I need to tell my sister.

27:30.080 --> 27:34.840
Did you learn those interrogation tricks
from my father's army?

27:36.760 --> 27:37.680
Not really.

27:39.400 --> 27:41.240
He advocated
for the humane treatment of captives.

27:42.040 --> 27:44.000
He'd never have used torture on them.

27:49.000 --> 27:50.080
Are you not afraid anymore?

27:50.840 --> 27:52.120
Why would I?

27:52.760 --> 27:54.560
I grew up in military camps.

27:54.640 --> 27:56.360
I've seen my share

27:57.120 --> 27:58.520
of slaughter and bloodshed.

28:06.880 --> 28:08.640
That is no blessing.

28:10.120 --> 28:11.280
Better to have never seen it at all.

28:17.400 --> 28:20.640
But in this life, who truly has a choice?

28:22.040 --> 28:25.080
I have no desire to kill,
yet they come for my life.

28:26.440 --> 28:32.880
I told you I kill
just so I can stay alive.

28:35.000 --> 28:38.280
I want to live to see my father again.

28:39.640 --> 28:40.520
I will do the killing for you.

28:46.720 --> 28:48.320
Hey. The ones after them

28:48.400 --> 28:51.520
belong to Xiao Xun,
heir to the Lord of Xiaonan.

28:52.480 --> 28:53.960
A humble meal

28:55.200 --> 28:56.760
in a humble place.

28:59.200 --> 29:00.760
I hope Your Highness can forgive me.

29:21.000 --> 29:22.680
You are the Grand Princess?

29:23.600 --> 29:26.760
No. You were supposed to marry
the heir to the Lord of Xiaonan.

29:28.680 --> 29:29.840
So you eloped with this man?

29:39.160 --> 29:40.480
Xiao Xun deceived me.

29:41.360 --> 29:42.880
Everything he wanted,

29:42.960 --> 29:46.040
from the very start,
was my father's command over the army.

29:47.280 --> 29:48.640
But I won't let him have it.

29:50.960 --> 29:52.120
Never ever.

29:52.880 --> 29:54.760
You're Chu Ling's daughter.

29:55.600 --> 29:58.000
Did he ever tell you who your mother was?

30:06.520 --> 30:09.200
Mr. Ge, you take quite an interest
in Yunzhong Prefecture.

30:10.240 --> 30:12.480
You even know every detail
of my betrothal.

30:13.160 --> 30:18.480
No wonder this stronghold
bears the marks of frontier troops.

30:28.680 --> 30:32.480
Since we're speaking so frankly,
ma'am, you might as well tell the truth.

30:33.000 --> 30:35.680
What really happened when my father went

30:37.200 --> 30:38.960
to Cangmu Stronghold?

30:39.840 --> 30:41.360
Nothing much.

30:42.400 --> 30:47.040
It's just
that General Chu killed our former leader.

30:47.720 --> 30:49.320
Then why do you still care
about him so much?

30:50.480 --> 30:53.720
Don't you want to avenge your leader?

31:00.960 --> 31:04.960
Back then, word got out
that we were raiding the frontier,

31:05.040 --> 31:06.840
so General Chu came to eradicate us.

31:07.640 --> 31:10.720
But after killing the former leader,
he realized it was all a misunderstanding.

31:11.880 --> 31:13.920
So he stepped in to resettle
the rest of us.

31:14.520 --> 31:16.000
Everything you see now

31:16.080 --> 31:19.600
is just your father's guilt
and his way of making amends.

31:21.120 --> 31:22.520
-But…
-The debt has been settled.

31:23.920 --> 31:25.360
There's no point bringing it up anymore.

31:29.080 --> 31:30.520
You've had a long journey.

31:30.600 --> 31:31.640
Why don't you try to get some rest?

31:32.360 --> 31:33.760
I'm right here if you need anything.

31:51.720 --> 31:53.440
They aren't like ordinary bandits.

31:54.320 --> 31:58.160
Their story about the General's campaign,
how he supposedly killed the innocents,

31:58.800 --> 32:00.400
is rather flimsy.

32:02.200 --> 32:04.000
Largely fiction, with a grain of truth.

32:06.320 --> 32:09.400
But I do believe my father
genuinely wanted to protect this place.

32:10.360 --> 32:15.000
And I'm certain they mean no harm to us.

32:15.600 --> 32:17.080
As for the rest…

32:17.600 --> 32:19.240
Everyone has secrets.

32:20.080 --> 32:23.920
When they'll finally come to light,
that's just a matter of fate.

32:30.840 --> 32:32.080
Wangcheng is just ahead.

32:32.160 --> 32:35.080
Past it lies Yunzhong Prefecture.

32:36.960 --> 32:38.680
Once we deal with Xiao Xun's men,

32:41.800 --> 32:43.080
you'll finally see your father.

32:45.440 --> 32:46.440
I know.

32:48.040 --> 32:49.120
I know this road

32:51.160 --> 32:52.400
all too well.

32:58.880 --> 32:59.920
<i>Back then,</i>

33:01.160 --> 33:03.000
<i>this was the exact path I took</i>

33:04.440 --> 33:05.840
<i>to be away from my father,</i>

33:07.960 --> 33:09.360
<i>Yunzhong Prefecture,</i>

33:10.880 --> 33:12.920
<i>and everything that held me dear,</i>

33:13.000 --> 33:14.920
<i>only to fall</i>

33:16.440 --> 33:18.480
<i>into the mire of eternal doom.</i>

33:43.360 --> 33:44.200
Jiu.

33:46.440 --> 33:48.640
If we had a second chance at life,

33:50.240 --> 33:52.360
would anything actually change?

34:01.760 --> 34:02.760
A second chance

34:04.640 --> 34:06.040
<i>at life…</i>

34:06.120 --> 34:06.760
GRACE AND BENEVOLENCE

34:09.159 --> 34:11.800
<i>‎Jiu, from now on, you have</i>
<i>‎a home here at Xie Residence.</i>

34:12.719 --> 34:14.639
<i>‎Mother!</i>

34:35.080 --> 34:36.239
Perhaps it wouldn't change a thing.

34:38.159 --> 34:39.440
But for me,

34:40.960 --> 34:42.360
things are already different.

34:45.719 --> 34:49.840
Remember that dream I told you about?

34:51.440 --> 34:52.920
<i>At the very end,</i>

34:54.120 --> 34:57.320
<i>someone killed Xiao Xun for me.</i>

34:59.840 --> 35:01.680
<i>Do you know who it was?</i>

35:03.840 --> 35:05.200
It was you.

35:13.640 --> 35:18.120
You killed him and avenged my family.

35:22.360 --> 35:23.600
But this time,

35:26.480 --> 35:28.120
I have to do it myself.

35:28.920 --> 35:31.440
Though fear may still echo in my chest,

35:33.160 --> 35:35.760
and a crumbling cliff awaits my next step,

35:36.360 --> 35:37.280
nothing in this world

35:40.320 --> 35:41.840
will hold me back.

36:18.480 --> 36:20.160
Whatever you fear in the days to come,

36:22.000 --> 36:25.960
whatever that dream may be, real or not,

36:27.920 --> 36:28.920
face it,

36:30.680 --> 36:31.640
grasp it,

36:33.080 --> 36:34.280
and conquer it.

36:40.840 --> 36:42.520
And the fear will leave you.

36:43.760 --> 36:44.920
I'm not terrified.

36:47.320 --> 36:48.760
My father and I

36:50.680 --> 36:52.480
will survive.
